name: Words
description: It makes me wonder a bit, are people purchasing the risk of displaying the word or the meaning behind the creation of the piece? Does the thrill of having a piece of art that so boldly flaunts the breaking of social custom justify the cost? To some, yes. To others, definitely not. Does it make you feel uncomfortable? Does it intrigue? Does it make you wonder? …ask any questions? Hopefully. And if not, it still says, fuck. Wessel ‘21
